Package buffalo3d.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDirtyManaged  
    IDirtyParent  
    IObject3dContainer
    Using Actionscript 3 nomenclature for what are essentially "pass-thru" methods to an underlying ArrayList
    IObject3dParent
    Defines the responsibilities for a class that will be a parent of a Object3d.
    IRendererGLSurfaceViewConfig
    Any GlSurfaceView settings that needs to be executed before GLSurfaceView.setRenderer() can be done by overriding this method.
    ISceneController
    Interface to handle the initialization of the Scene and the 'on-enter-frame' updates to the Scene (think 'model').
